doctype html
html(lang='ru')
  +head('../','VIDEO 28')
  link(rel="stylesheet", href="../css/ekko-lightbox.css")
  body
    +header("../")
    main
      +slider('../')
      .container.videos
        .row.mx-auto
          .col
            h3 VIDEO 28 
            h4 Mixed Wrestling - the Best Fights. Part 3.  2013
            p.
              This is the third video of the series titled "<b>Mixed wrestling - the best fights</b>". Here you can see two separate wrestling matches of <b>Tais</b> (5'7" / 132 lb) against two male opponents: <b>Villian</b> (5'8" / 177 lb) and <b>Alexander</b> (5’10’’ / 205 lb). Although Tais is a strong and experienced fighter, she had a tough time in these fights, especially against big Alexander who was 73 lb heavier than her.
            img.mainImg(src='../img/videos/28/main.jpg' alt='main')
            p.
              To find out what was the result of this uneven challenge, watch this video.
            h5 Tais vs Alexander
            a.btn.btn-primary.screensBtn(data-toggle='collapse' href='#collapseExample' role='button' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample')
              | SCREENSHOTS
            #collapseExample.collapse
              .col-md-12.text-center
                  .row.justify-content-center
                    - var n = 0;
                    while n < 2
                      - n = n+1
                      a.col-sm-4(href='../img/videos/28/tais-alexander/'+n+'.jpg' data-toggle='lightbox' data-gallery='example-gallery')
                        img.img-fluid(src='../img/videos/28/tais-alexander/'+n+'.jpg')
            h5 Tais vs Villian
            a.btn.btn-primary.screensBtn(data-toggle='collapse' href='#collapseExample3' role='button' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample')
              | SCREENSHOTS
            #collapseExample3.collapse
              .col-md-12.text-center
                  .row.justify-content-center
